schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
type Event {
  _id: ID!
  nom: String
  image: String
  informations: String
  description: String
  nbpersonnes: Int
  organisateur: String
  date: String
  participants: [String]
}

type Query {
  events: [Event]
  event(_id: ID!): Event
}

type Mutation {
  createEvent(
    nom: String
    image: String
    informations: String
    description: String
    nbpersonnes: Int
    organisateur: String
    date: String
    participants: [String]
  ): Event!

  updateEvent(
    _id: ID!
    nom: String
    image: String
    informations: String
    description: String
    nbpersonnes: Int
    organisateur: String
    date: String
    participants: [String]
  ): Event!

  addParticipant(_id_event: ID, username: String): Event!
}
